{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting this property to ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocationVisible"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Your app must specify a value for ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription"},{"text":" or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription"},{"text":" in its ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Info.plist"},{"text":" to satisfy the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"locationManager"},{"type":"text","text":" before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"showsUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"showsUserLocation","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"title":"MLNMapVi